::DeathScythe/Ramulus::

DeathScythe chuckles to himself. He was above the new bot, as the scanners 
reported. He slows down slightly, continuing to fly above SnowCat.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus nods. "Good. I am too."

He dodges a tree, continuing to gallop. "There's an enemy chasing you, you 
probably know that by now. Can you make it to the nearest clearing?"

He knew that she would be in more danger in a clearing, but if he could get 
there, he was sure that he could fight DeathScythe off.
